{
    "success": true,
    "data": {
        "version_number": 1,
        "sub_format": "json",
        "subtitles": [
            {
                "start": 29660,
                "text": "We all know that the world is in a<br>very serious environmental crisis today.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": true,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": 37360,
                "position": 1
            },
            {
                "start": 38398,
                "text": "We also know that we are in a great hurry.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": 41998,
                "position": 2
            },
            {
                "start": 42053,
                "text": "We do not have too much time<br>to think and change the strategies.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": 49203,
                "position": 3
            },
            {
                "start": 49495,
                "text": "We probably have decades of time.<br>We do not have centuries of time.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": 56265,
                "position": 4
            },
            {
                "start": 57575,
                "text": "So I begin with that.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": 59655,
                "position": 5
            },
            {
                "start": 60744,
                "text": "The first thing we should do<br>is to change the attitude",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": 65474,
                "position": 6
            },
            {
                "start": 65748,
                "text": "towards the planet and the world.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": 69488,
                "position": 7
            },
            {
                "start": 70887,
                "text": "We should think that the planet is sick",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": 74227,
                "position": 8
            },
            {
                "start": 74443,
                "text": "and that it is a patient,",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": 76053,
                "position": 9
            },
            {
                "start": 77152,
                "text": "and human beings, the mankind, is the disease.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": 82932,
                "position": 10
            },
            {
                "start": 84033,
                "text": "We should no longer be the disease.<br>We should be the doctor.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": 88343,
                "position": 11
            },
            {
                "start": 90495,
                "text": "This is why I will present<br>three different strategies",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": 96165,
                "position": 12
            },
            {
                "start": 96222,
                "text": "which can be realized simultaneously.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": 99202,
                "position": 13
            },
            {
                "start": 100195,
                "text": "I will take healthcare as a comparison.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": 103665,
                "position": 14
            },
            {
                "start": 106081,
                "text": "The first strategy should begin very quickly",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": 110801,
                "position": 15
            },
            {
                "start": 111029,
                "text": "and it cannot last for a long time.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": 114389,
                "position": 16
            },
            {
                "start": 117583,
                "text": "I would call that 'the first aid' of this sickness.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": 124293,
                "position": 17
            },
            {
                "start": 125682,
                "text": "We have an immense number of resources<br>on earth.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": 130712,
                "position": 18
            },
            {
                "start": 131416,
                "text": "We have a lot of armies",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": 133316,
                "position": 19
            },
            {
                "start": 134518,
                "text": "and they cost about 1,500 billion dollars per year.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": 143898,
                "position": 20
            },
            {
                "start": 146032,
                "text": "1,500 billion dollars.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": 149032,
                "position": 21
            },
            {
                "start": 150309,
                "text": "The goal of all that money is to destroy and to kill.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": 158959,
                "position": 22
            },
            {
                "start": 159609,
                "text": "Destroy other armies.<br>Destroy and kill other people and cities.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": 166709,
                "position": 23
            },
            {
                "start": 168098,
                "text": "So, my first suggestion here is that",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": 172328,
                "position": 24
            },
            {
                "start": 172852,
                "text": "we should joined the armies.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": 175142,
                "position": 25
            },
            {
                "start": 176820,
                "text": "We should declare a new war,",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": 179860,
                "position": 26
            },
            {
                "start": 180675,
                "text": "not between the armies,<br>not one army against another army,",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": 187045,
                "position": 27
            },
            {
                "start": 187680,
                "text": "but we should declare a defensive war",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": 191280,
                "position": 28
            },
            {
                "start": 191905,
                "text": "on how we should take care<br>of the dangers of the future.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": 197145,
                "position": 29
            },
            {
                "start": 198239,
                "text": "In this way, we could give tasks to the armies.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": 202989,
                "position": 30
            },
            {
                "start": 203288,
                "text": "The armies are good<br>because they obey the tasks.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": 207288,
                "position": 31
            },
            {
                "start": 208358,
                "text": "The armies are not so good in that<br>they don't protest and they are not democratic.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": 213058,
                "position": 32
            },
            {
                "start": 213058,
                "text": "They do what they're told to do.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": 215428,
                "position": 33
            },
            {
                "start": 216356,
                "text": "We could give them the task to reforest Sahara.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": 224146,
                "position": 34
            },
            {
                "start": 226118,
                "text": "Then the task that seems impossible<br>will become possible.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": 231588,
                "position": 35
            },
            {
                "start": 232780,
                "text": "The reforestation in Sahara",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": 236090,
                "position": 36
            },
            {
                "start": 236652,
                "text": "costs about one sixth of the resourses<br>used today in these armies.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": 247022,
                "position": 37
            },
            {
                "start": 248210,
                "text": "So my first suggestion is to join the armies.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": 252690,
                "position": 38
            },
            {
                "start": 252730,
                "text": "Declare a new kind of war.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": 255250,
                "position": 39
            },
            {
                "start": 258403,
                "text": "Then comes the next step, 'Use your healthcare.'",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": 267113,
                "position": 40
            },
            {
                "start": 268659,
                "text": "We have a wrong kind of production.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": 271879,
                "position": 41
            },
            {
                "start": 272941,
                "text": "We produce things but we do not plan<br>or make the design work properly,",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": 282811,
                "position": 42
            },
            {
                "start": 283601,
                "text": "as mentioned in the earlier speech.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": 287961,
                "position": 43
            },
            {
                "start": 290004,
                "text": "So we need a new kind of industrial revolution.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": 294004,
                "position": 44
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "That revolution must change all the different parts",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 45
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "of the production and the consumption<br>at the same time.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 46
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "It has to change the traffic.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 47
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "We cannot use the cars anymore.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 48
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "It has to change the energy production.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 49
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "The energy production can no longer have<br>CO2 emission to the atmosphere.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 50
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "The land used must be renewed",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 51
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "so that we have food produced<br>close to where people live.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 52
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "The whole production must be based<br>on recycling.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 53
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "So all these different sectors of production<br>must change.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 54
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "How can they change?",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 55
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "They can actually change, in the best way,<br>by building the so-called 'eco-cities'.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 56
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "In an eco-city, all these different changes<br>are taken into consideration simultaneously.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 57
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "For example, while producing an electric car,",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 58
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "if the electricity is produced in another place<br>by burning coal,",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 59
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "then there is still the emission of CO2 like before.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 60
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "So there is a comprehensive change<br>in everything.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 61
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "When we design and plan new kinds of cities,",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 62
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "all these should be taken into consideration<br>simultaneously.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 63
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "Another thing is, when we plan the new cities",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 64
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "we must also take into consideration<br>the cities that already exist.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 65
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "Cities like London, Paris, Beijing, Lagos in Africa<br>and Mexico should also be changed.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 66
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "That is a much greater job than building<br>a new city in a virgin environment.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 67
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "We must develop a strategy to build new cities",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 68
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "while taking into consideration<br>energy, traffic, land use and production.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 69
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "We have think about what we would do<br>to the cities in which we are living today.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 70
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "For example, if we say Paris must change,",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 71
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "it doesn't mean that we would get rid of<br>all the buildings and streets,",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 72
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "but it means that the whole infrastructure<br>must completely change.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 73
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "The system of traffic must change<br>so there are no more cars.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 74
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "The change that is similar to<br>when they changed from horses to cars.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 75
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "Traffic systems that do not pollute the atmosphere.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 76
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "Energy production in Paris must also change<br>completely, and so on.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 77
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "The infrastructure of the old cities should change.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 78
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "Now the last point.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 79
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "Preventive cure.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 80
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "The preventive cure is the slowest of these three.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 81
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "The preventive cure involves<br>completely changing our values",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 82
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "for the next generation.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 83
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "Our values are too materialistic.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 84
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "We must renew the values.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 85
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "We must have more spiritual values.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 86
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "We must appreciate different things<br>than what we appreciate today.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 87
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "A big car is ridiculous, for example.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 88
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "You should not waste things.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 89
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "You should use your objects until the end,<br>as presented earlier.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 90
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "That is the main question, actually.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 91
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "I don't believe that can be changed",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 92
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "in the next few years<br>or even in the next twenty years.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 93
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "But it can absolutely be changed<br>by the future generations.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 94
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "The future generation will change their values.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 95
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "We have a very good foundation<br>for the other two strategies,",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 96
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "which I will propose here.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 97
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "I think there are two ways of changing the world.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 98
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "The first is, 'from grassroots upwards'.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 99
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "This is what everyone can do individually.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 100
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "Everyone can do this,<br>by considering their manners of consumption.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 101
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "And that would already<br>be the start of something.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 102
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "I must confess that I am a criminal.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 103
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "Ah, yes. (laughter) Criminal.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 104
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "A criminal speaking to you.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 105
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "I drive a car daily, you know?",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 106
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "I eat meat from an animal. (laughter)",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 107
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "I have more than two children. <br>That is the worst thing.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 108
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "I have more than two pairs of shoes.<br>Can you imagine?",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 109
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "More than two pairs of shoes.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 110
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "So from grassroots upwards,<br>I am not in the position to give you any advice.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 111
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "The other thing is that<br>we try to influence the powerful people",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 112
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "to change their minds by discussing with them,<br>by teaching them",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 113
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "because they are not the most intelligent people,<br>those powerful people.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 114
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "Teaching them how they should<br>actually change the world.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 115
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "I cannot boast.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 116
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "I was told how to speak, how not to speak,",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 117
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "what to say and what not to say.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 118
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "I got very strict instructions.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 119
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "So I am not telling anything about myself.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 120
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "I will tell you about Mr Somebody<br>who has done something.<br>",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 121
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "Mr Somebody.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 122
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "The first story was in 1980,",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 123
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "when Mr Somebody and his friend<br>decided at a pub in Helsinki",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 124
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "that the Islamic architecture<br>must somehow remain in the world.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 125
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "The Arabic countries back then had oil and money",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 126
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "and they wanted to employ<br>all the Western planners and constructors",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 127
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "to change their cities.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 128
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "And that seemed to be a distraction<br>to the Islamic architecture.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 129
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "After 6 months, we were, no sorry. (laughter)",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 130
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "After 6 months, when Mr Somebody and his friends",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 131
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "were sitting at the pub in Helsinki<br>and talking about that,",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 132
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "there was a range in Baghdad,",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 133
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "a big conference with high officials<br>from all the Arabic countries",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 134
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "talking about how to preserve<br>the Islamic architecture.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 135
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "There was a guy whose name was Saddam Hussein.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 136
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "He was the president of Iraq at the time.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 137
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "A young handsome guy.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 138
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "He showed up everyday,",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 139
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "opened the whole conference<br>and spoke very wisely.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 140
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "He had gotten good instructions<br>from Mr Somebody.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 141
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "Two days after the conference was over,",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 142
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "Mr Hussein began a war against Iran.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 143
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "Everything then on is history, as you know.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 144
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "But the seed was cultivated anyhow.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 145
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "All those high officials<br>from different Arabic countries",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 146
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "began to think this over.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 147
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "Next case.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 148
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "The Finnish Parliamentarians are similar<br>to those in other countries.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 149
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "They think four years ahead to the next election.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 150
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "That is a pity because<br>they should think more ahead.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 151
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "Decades ahead.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 152
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "For this reason, a new committee was created<br>in the Finnish Parliament,",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 153
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "which was the first in the world,",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 154
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "and it is now an official part<br>of the Finnish Parliament.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 155
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "That committee has a task of<br>only thinking about longterm questions.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 156
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "But again, there is a problem.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 157
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "The problem is that<br>the everyday legislation does not follow",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 158
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "those longterm visions<br>that the future committee has.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 159
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "But that probably will also change.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 160
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "Number three.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 161
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "Development aid in Africa has been criticized<br>for a long, long time.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 162
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "That's why Mr Somebody made about twenty trips<br>to Sub-Saharan Africa,",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 163
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "wrote a book about those trips<br>and came to a conclusion.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 164
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "What should be done with Africa?",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 165
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "Now I ask you, what are the four issues<br>that are most important?",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 166
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "Environment? No?",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 167
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "Education? Hands up if you think so.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 168
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "Family planning? Government? Okay.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 169
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "It's time for the last topic.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 170
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "China is the next topic.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 171
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "China has begun to build eco-cities.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 172
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "The eco-cities combine all the new technology,",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 173
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "and that is the first step<br>to the new kind of production.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 174
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "But even then, they make too many compromises.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 175
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "The compromises somehow diminish<br>the value of these cities.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 176
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "But at least it is another step forward.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 177
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "It seems to be that we have the dream,<br>so we take two steps forward.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 178
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "Then comes the reality,<br>and we take one step backward.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 179
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "But in the end, at least we have taken one step forward.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 180
            },
            {
                "start": null,
                "text": "Remember that. Thank you.",
                "meta": {
                    "new_paragraph": false,
                    "region": null
                },
                "end": null,
                "position": 181
            }
